Interface SessionFactoryOptions

        String getUuid()
        Get the UUID unique to this SessionFactoryOptions. Will be the same value available as SessionFactoryImplementor.getUuid().
        Returns:
        The UUID for this SessionFactory.
        See Also:
        SessionFactoryRegistry.getSessionFactory(java.lang.String), SessionFactoryImplementor.getUuid()

        boolean isJpaBootstrap()
        Was building of the SessionFactory initiated through JPA bootstrapping, or through Hibernate's native bootstrapping?
        Returns:
        true indicates the SessionFactory was built through JPA bootstrapping; false indicates it was built through native bootstrapping.
